  <summary date="2019-11-27T15:40:14Z" status="Introduced in House">Fair Pay for All Act of 2019

This bill prohibits sex discrimination in the payment of the minimum wage to workers based on their gender identity, sexual orientation, sex characteristics, a sex stereotype, pregnancy, childbirth, or a related medical condition.</summary>
